            . I manage my mother's business - she keeps town-carts in Thames-street. I was going up Lawrence Pountney-lane, and heard a person call after Mr. Man that his pocket was picked; I then turned round, and saw the prisoner on the other side of the way; I laid hold of him, and held him till Mr. Man came, and I saw him take the handkerchief from his breast.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
